## Test plan

### Integration (`server/tests/integration/__APP_ID__.test.ts`)
- boots + migrates
- registers all tools + faces
- For each tool, one `it(...)`: call `execute`, assert return shape AND DB state
- For each face, one `it(...)`: seed rows, call resolver, assert output matches the declared shape
- For each delete/update tool, one "not-found returns error" case

### E2E (`server/tests/e2e/test___APP_ID_UNDERSCORE__.py`)
- `test_launcher_lists_app` — `__APP_NAME__` visible in device panel
- `test_compact_face_renders` — on default device (watch), initial expected text visible
- `test_expanded_variant_renders` — switch to phone, TopBar title visible
- `test_tool_invocation_updates_face` — invoke a tool, reload, face reflects mutation
